resources.description:
Returns players of a specific team passed in by way of request parameter, the string is passed into an SQL query within the JPA repo to retrieve rows that fit this request

```response
{
  "players": [
    {
      "id": 122,
      "team": "bos",
      "jersey_number": "19",
      "name": "Hirokazu Sawamura",
      "position": "Pitcher"
    },
    {
      "id": 123,
      "team": "bos",
      "jersey_number": "37",
      "name": "Nick Pivetta",
      "position": "Pitcher"
    }
  ],
  "team": {
    "id": 4,
    "team_name": "Boston Red Sox",
    "team_abr": "bos",
    "conference": "American League",
    "division": "AL East"
  }
}
```

Returns a specified player by ID and then makes another request to retrieve the team data from the Team database using the abbreviation of the specified players "team" field

```response
